{"tha-ap481:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap481:0.2":"Nalamalivagga ","tha-ap481:0.3":"Panadhidayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap481:1.1":"“Anomadassi bhagava, ","tha-ap481:1.2":"lokajettho narasabho; ","tha-ap481:1.3":"Divavihara nikkhamma, ","tha-ap481:1.4":"pathamaruhi cakkhuma. ","tha-ap481:2.1":"Panadhim sukatam gayha, ","tha-ap481:2.2":"addhanam patipajjaham; ","tha-ap481:2.3":"Tatthaddasasim sambuddham, ","tha-ap481:2.4":"pattikam carudassanam. ","tha-ap481:3.1":"Sakam cittam pasadetva, ","tha-ap481:3.2":"niharitvana panadhim; ","tha-ap481:3.3":"Padamule thapetvana, ","tha-ap481:3.4":"idam vacanamabravim. ","tha-ap481:4.1":"‘Abhiruha mahavira, ","tha-ap481:4.2":"sugatinda vinayaka; ","tha-ap481:4.3":"Ito phalam labhissami, ","tha-ap481:4.4":"so me attho samijjhatu’. ","tha-ap481:5.1":"Anomadassi bhagava, ","tha-ap481:5.2":"lokajettho narasabho; ","tha-ap481:5.3":"Panadhim abhiruhitva, ","tha-ap481:5.4":"idam vacanamabravi. ","tha-ap481:6.1":"‘Yo panadhim me adasi, ","tha-ap481:6.2":"pasanno sehi panibhi; ","tha-ap481:6.3":"Tamaham kittayissami, ","tha-ap481:6.4":"sunatha mama bhasato’. ","tha-ap481:7.1":"Buddhassa giramannaya, ","tha-ap481:7.2":"sabbe deva samagata; ","tha-ap481:7.3":"Udaggacitta sumana, ","tha-ap481:7.4":"vedajata katanjali. ","tha-ap481:8.1":"‘Panadhinam padanena, ","tha-ap481:8.2":"sukhitoyam bhavissati; ","tha-ap481:8.3":"Pancapannasakkhattunca, ","tha-ap481:8.4":"devarajjam karissati. ","tha-ap481:9.1":"Sahassakkhattum raja ca, ","tha-ap481:9.2":"cakkavatti bhavissati; ","tha-ap481:9.3":"Padesarajjam vipulam, ","tha-ap481:9.4":"gananato asankhiyam. ","tha-ap481:10.1":"Aparimeyye ito kappe, ","tha-ap481:10.2":"okkakakulasambhavo; ","tha-ap481:10.3":"Gotamo nama gottena, ","tha-ap481:10.4":"sattha loke bhavissati. ","tha-ap481:11.1":"Tassa dhammesu dayado, ","tha-ap481:11.2":"oraso dhammanimmito; ","tha-ap481:11.3":"Sabbasave parinnaya, ","tha-ap481:11.4":"nibbayissatinasavo. ","tha-ap481:12.1":"Devaloke manusse va, ","tha-ap481:12.2":"nibbattissati punnava; ","tha-ap481:12.3":"Devayanapatibhagam, ","tha-ap481:12.4":"yanam patilabhissati’. ","tha-ap481:13.1":"Pasada sivika vayham, ","tha-ap481:13.2":"hatthino samalankata; ","tha-ap481:13.3":"Ratha vajannasamyutta, ","tha-ap481:13.4":"sada patubhavanti me. ","tha-ap481:14.1":"Agara nikkhamantopi, ","tha-ap481:14.2":"rathena nikkhamim aham; ","tha-ap481:14.3":"Kesesu chijjamanesu, ","tha-ap481:14.4":"arahattamapapunim. ","tha-ap481:15.1":"Labha mayham suladdham me, ","tha-ap481:15.2":"vanijjam suppayojitam; ","tha-ap481:15.3":"Datvana panadhim ekam, ","tha-ap481:15.4":"pattomhi acalam padam. ","tha-ap481:16.1":"Aparimeyye ito kappe, ","tha-ap481:16.2":"yam panadhimadasaham; ","tha-ap481:16.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap481:16.4":"panadhissa idam phalam. ","tha-ap481:17.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap481:17.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap481:17.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap481:18.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap481:18.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap481:18.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap481:19.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap481:19.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap481:19.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap481:20.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma panadhidayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap481:21.1":"Panadhidayakattherassapadanam navamam. "}